24 SECTION 2. Arkansas Code Title 26, Chapter 51, Subchapter 3, is
25 amended to add an additional section to read as follows:
26 26-51-317. Bonuses.
27 (a) As used in this section, "bonus" means a payment made to an
28 employee that:
29 (1) Is in addition to the employee’s regular or overtime wages;
30 (2) Is nonrecurring;
31 (3) Does not increase the employee’s base rate of pay; and
32 (4) Includes no commitment for payment in a subsequent year.
33 (b) A bonus is exempt from the income tax levied under this chapter.
34
35 SECTION 3. EFFECTIVE DATE. Section 1 of this act is effective for tax
36 years beginning on or after January 1, 2026.
